1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:46,000
=Episode 25=

16
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:12,340
Sir.

17
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:13,060
Welcome.

18
00:02:13,540 --> 00:02:14,780
Please have a seat.

19
00:02:18,901 --> 00:02:19,380
Right here.

20
00:02:32,741 --> 00:02:33,540
Dongchao

21
00:02:34,301 --> 00:02:37,540
has been asking me to invite you.

22
00:02:38,380 --> 00:02:39,181
I've previously

23
00:02:39,581 --> 00:02:41,380
made a public commitment

24
00:02:42,060 --> 00:02:43,861
to fully support you, Sir.

25
00:02:44,261 --> 00:02:45,701
The reason I did so

26
00:02:46,141 --> 00:02:49,181
was for the sake of
Bosi Real Estate's future development.

27
00:02:50,421 --> 00:02:52,301
Regarding the tripartite cooperation

28
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,741
I mentioned to you before,

29
00:02:54,421 --> 00:02:56,380
I have given it
a thorough consideration.

30
00:02:56,741 --> 00:02:59,780
I believe this is the best possible path

31
00:02:59,981 --> 00:03:01,380
for Bosi Real Estate.

32
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:13,220
Grandmother and Mr. Jiang

33
00:03:13,421 --> 00:03:15,421
have come to meet you
with total sincerity.

34
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:16,380
You should still

35
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:17,500
keep up with the times, Sir.

36
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,720
You should put down your pride

37
00:03:18,901 --> 00:03:20,540
and accept the new rules of the game.

38
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,820
For the sake of Bosi's future,

39
00:03:23,021 --> 00:03:24,100
it wouldn't hurt to listen

40
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:26,021
to Grandmother and Mr. Jiang's plan.

41
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:30,181
It's not your turn to speak here.

42
00:03:32,021 --> 00:03:33,741
How could you
talk to Sir Yang like that?

43
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,141
Get out.

44
00:03:40,380 --> 00:03:41,500
I'm sorry, Sir.

45
00:03:45,940 --> 00:03:47,060
Young people these days...

46
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:48,981
They also show such insolence.

47
00:03:50,141 --> 00:03:50,940
Sir,

48
00:03:51,540 --> 00:03:52,820
please don't mind her.

49
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,900
For the transformation
of Bosi Real Estate,

50
00:03:57,380 --> 00:03:59,820
you've put in painstaking effort.

51
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:02,620
But what is your ultimate goal?

52
00:04:05,901 --> 00:04:06,981
If you ask me,

53
00:04:07,620 --> 00:04:08,901
Sir Yang is trying to use

54
00:04:09,581 --> 00:04:11,220
existing residential renovation projects

55
00:04:11,340 --> 00:04:12,780
to pivot from commercial real estate

56
00:04:12,780 --> 00:04:14,340
to residential housing.

57
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:15,701
Am I right?

58
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:17,821
What are you getting at?

59
00:04:18,941 --> 00:04:19,740
Right.

60
00:04:21,061 --> 00:04:22,980
Actually, I've always understood

61
00:04:22,980 --> 00:04:24,061
the effort you've put in.

62
00:04:24,901 --> 00:04:25,740
In this city alone,

63
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:27,220
aging residential property

64
00:04:27,701 --> 00:04:29,461
exceeds 220 million square meters.

65
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:31,540
These buildings are outdated

66
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:32,381
and inefficient.

67
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:35,100
You've spotted the potential
in the massive market

68
00:04:35,100 --> 00:04:36,141
of residential renovation.

69
00:04:37,461 --> 00:04:38,701
If we pull this off,

70
00:04:38,941 --> 00:04:41,180
it will certainly be

71
00:04:41,501 --> 00:04:43,141
a noble cause
for our country and people.

72
00:04:50,461 --> 00:04:52,100
But in our industry,

73
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:54,540
not many are willing

74
00:04:56,021 --> 00:04:56,901
to take that leap.

75
00:04:58,180 --> 00:04:58,980
True.

76
00:05:00,220 --> 00:05:01,021
However,

77
00:05:02,420 --> 00:05:03,980
Ms. Bai always reminds us

78
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:05,461
to be a business for the people,

79
00:05:05,621 --> 00:05:07,261
striving for the public good.

80
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:08,941
From that perspective,

81
00:05:09,941 --> 00:05:11,501
our visions are perfectly aligned.

82
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:14,220
I don't just support your

83
00:05:14,381 --> 00:05:16,660
residential renovation plan.

84
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:18,501
I want to evolve it into

85
00:05:18,501 --> 00:05:19,980
a larger-scale concept

86
00:05:19,980 --> 00:05:21,540
for green real estate.

87
00:05:22,501 --> 00:05:23,061
That way,

88
00:05:23,061 --> 00:05:24,740
we can ensure everyone nationwide

89
00:05:24,980 --> 00:05:26,941
benefits from this social welfare.

90
00:05:27,701 --> 00:05:28,501
If all three parties

91
00:05:28,501 --> 00:05:29,701
can secure this partnership,

92
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:30,901
we can open up financing

93
00:05:30,901 --> 00:05:31,860
to the entire public.

94
00:05:32,141 --> 00:05:33,061
When that happens,

95
00:05:33,780 --> 00:05:35,100
it won't just be this project.

96
00:05:35,980 --> 00:05:37,540
All of your ideals, Sir Yang,

97
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:40,581
can finally become a reality.

98
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:44,701
What you just said

99
00:05:45,901 --> 00:05:48,021
mirrors exactly what

100
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:50,701
Rao Yuci told me.

101
00:05:51,300 --> 00:05:52,381
Rao Yuci?

102
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:57,540
(Two days ago,
Xinkang Treatment Center)

103
00:06:06,261 --> 00:06:07,860
So this is Sir Yang.

104
00:06:07,901 --> 00:06:08,701
Yang.

105
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:10,461
I'm so jealous.

106
00:06:10,740 --> 00:06:11,860
It's been years,

107
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:13,740
yet you're still as vibrant as ever.

108
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:14,860
Looking sharp.

109
00:06:16,061 --> 00:06:17,261
Is that you?

110
00:06:21,461 --> 00:06:22,420
Long time no see.

111
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:23,980
Is this where you've been living?

112
00:06:26,461 --> 00:06:29,061
No wonder I haven't heard
from you all these years.

113
00:06:30,501 --> 00:06:31,941
It's a long story.

114
00:06:32,821 --> 00:06:34,300
But first, let me introduce someone.

115
00:06:35,621 --> 00:06:37,621
Yuci, come here.

116
00:06:43,021 --> 00:06:43,941
And she is...

117
00:06:44,300 --> 00:06:45,381
My goddaughter.

118
00:06:48,141 --> 00:06:49,180
Hello, Mr. Yang.

119
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:49,860
Hello.

120
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:50,901
I'm Rao Yuci.

121
00:06:51,821 --> 00:06:52,621
Nice to meet you.

122
00:06:57,261 --> 00:06:58,381
She came to me.

123
00:06:58,941 --> 00:06:59,901
I thought

124
00:07:00,261 --> 00:07:02,220
she was a lobbyist sent by Lysen Group.

125
00:07:05,980 --> 00:07:06,821
You misunderstood.

126
00:07:06,821 --> 00:07:08,300
That wasn't our intention at all.

127
00:07:10,860 --> 00:07:11,860
She's just young.

128
00:07:12,261 --> 00:07:13,660
Quick-witted and a bit outspoken.

129
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:14,980
Please don't take it to heart.

130
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:18,061
As an industrialist,

131
00:07:18,621 --> 00:07:19,701
we need you to step forward

132
00:07:20,261 --> 00:07:22,300
to ensure the financing is a success.

133
00:07:26,381 --> 00:07:27,180
Qingyu.

134
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:28,941
Mr. Jiang.

135
00:07:31,021 --> 00:07:31,821
Perhaps...

136
00:07:34,941 --> 00:07:36,821
Perhaps you were right all along.

137
00:07:38,141 --> 00:07:38,941
Dongchao.

138
00:07:40,261 --> 00:07:41,901
Sir Yang has given his word.

139
00:07:41,901 --> 00:07:44,061
Hurry up and raise a glass to him.

140
00:07:44,061 --> 00:07:44,780
Right, of course.

141
00:07:44,941 --> 00:07:46,061
To you, Sir Yang.

142
00:07:46,941 --> 00:07:48,660
I'll drink to that.

143
00:07:49,901 --> 00:07:51,581
Count Baiye Group in as well.

144
00:07:52,340 --> 00:07:54,220
Sir Yang, cheers.

145
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:10,141
Hello?

146
00:08:10,540 --> 00:08:12,100
Hello, is this Bai Liangliang?

147
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:12,860
Speaking.

148
00:08:13,021 --> 00:08:14,420
This is Luhu Police Station.

149
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,780
Is Bai Xia your mother?

150
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:18,821
There was an accident involving her.

151
00:08:20,740 --> 00:08:21,420
A cleaner

152
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:22,740
found her body

153
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:24,300
while cleaning the water.

154
00:08:24,501 --> 00:08:26,180
We've reviewed the surveillance footage

155
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:26,980
and found no sign

156
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:29,100
of anyone following her.

157
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:30,860
Furthermore, your mother's body

158
00:08:30,860 --> 00:08:32,981
shows no signs of external trauma.

159
00:08:33,060 --> 00:08:34,540
Therefore, our preliminary ruling

160
00:08:34,741 --> 00:08:35,660
is that your mother

161
00:08:35,741 --> 00:08:37,300
died from an accidental drowning.

162
00:09:08,021 --> 00:09:09,180
Is everything ready?

163
00:09:10,180 --> 00:09:11,021
Follow me, please.

164
00:09:22,741 --> 00:09:23,580
Sorry for your loss.

165
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:58,420
I brought you some flowers.

166
00:10:06,381 --> 00:10:07,261
You've probably

167
00:10:07,261 --> 00:10:08,780
never received any in your life.

168
00:10:14,861 --> 00:10:16,820
What a pathetic existence you led.

169
00:10:19,381 --> 00:10:21,341
It's exactly
the kind of life I fear most.

170
00:10:29,460 --> 00:10:31,381
I always wanted to prove myself to you.

171
00:10:34,420 --> 00:10:36,180
To show you my success.

172
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:40,621
To show you that I've defeated Rao Yuci.

173
00:10:42,021 --> 00:10:43,660
I'm almost there.

174
00:10:56,501 --> 00:10:58,580
Since you couldn't
give me the life I wanted,

175
00:10:59,621 --> 00:11:01,261
I decided to rewrite it myself.

176
00:11:03,420 --> 00:11:05,660
I can lead a glamorous life.

177
00:11:08,981 --> 00:11:10,021
I can even make sure

178
00:11:10,021 --> 00:11:11,501
you live with your head held high.

179
00:11:12,341 --> 00:11:14,381
Don't you like beautiful clothes?

180
00:11:16,501 --> 00:11:17,780
When you posed as Madam Bai

181
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:19,060
of the Beauty Pearl Society,

182
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:22,660
didn't you long
for a different kind of life?

183
00:11:39,020 --> 00:11:43,420
(Property Ownership Certificate
of the People's Republic of China)

184
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:44,381
This is the deed to

185
00:11:44,381 --> 00:11:45,901
No. 88 Linwei Alley.

186
00:11:47,261 --> 00:11:49,300
I changed the name back a long time ago.

187
00:11:50,060 --> 00:11:51,180
This house

188
00:11:51,981 --> 00:11:53,780
still belongs to you and Mr. Xu.

189
00:11:55,501 --> 00:11:56,341
I know

190
00:11:57,580 --> 00:11:58,621
this house

191
00:11:59,621 --> 00:12:01,621
holds all of your memories.

192
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:03,300
This house

193
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:05,021
means everything to you.

194
00:12:08,101 --> 00:12:10,101
I didn't take your house away.

195
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:20,780
(Property Ownership Certificate
of the People's Republic of China)

196
00:12:21,261 --> 00:12:22,381
And this card...

197
00:12:31,621 --> 00:12:33,660
What I said that day was out of anger.

198
00:12:34,341 --> 00:12:35,141
Bai Xia,

199
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:37,460
the money on this card

200
00:12:37,540 --> 00:12:40,101
is enough to buy three houses
like No. 88 Linwei Alley.

201
00:12:40,261 --> 00:12:41,141
Take it,

202
00:12:41,141 --> 00:12:42,940
and take Mr. Xu away from here.

203
00:12:43,180 --> 00:12:44,180
Leave this city.

204
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:45,621
Leave my life.

205
00:12:45,901 --> 00:12:47,501
And never come back.

206
00:12:54,221 --> 00:12:55,780
Bai Liangliang!

207
00:13:02,141 --> 00:13:03,221
Take your money.

208
00:13:04,300 --> 00:13:05,660
I don't need your pity!

209
00:13:07,180 --> 00:13:08,660
Ever since I started working,

210
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:10,341
I'd save

211
00:13:11,221 --> 00:13:13,261
some money into it every year.

212
00:13:14,381 --> 00:13:16,700
After so many years,

213
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:19,861
this is the retirement fund
I saved for you.

214
00:13:20,501 --> 00:13:21,460
It's yours.

215
00:13:21,981 --> 00:13:23,460
I prepared this for you.

216
00:13:37,381 --> 00:13:37,901
Liang.

217
00:13:38,700 --> 00:13:39,501
Mom made

218
00:13:39,501 --> 00:13:40,981
your favorite corn porridge.

219
00:13:44,780 --> 00:13:45,381
Liang.

220
00:13:57,101 --> 00:13:58,540
Wake up.

221
00:14:00,901 --> 00:14:02,420
Wake up and talk to me.

222
00:14:02,420 --> 00:14:03,700
Wake up!

223
00:14:34,221 --> 00:14:35,021
(Liangliang.)

224
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:37,861
(In this life,)

225
00:14:39,141 --> 00:14:40,460
(I'm content with)

226
00:14:40,460 --> 00:14:41,460
(a peaceful life)

227
00:14:42,741 --> 00:14:43,741
and someone who is

228
00:14:44,820 --> 00:14:46,580
genuinely good to both of us.

229
00:14:47,621 --> 00:14:48,981
That's enough for me.

230
00:14:50,901 --> 00:14:53,221
This girl gets more difficult
the older she grows.

231
00:14:55,021 --> 00:14:55,820
Take this.

232
00:14:55,901 --> 00:14:57,381
Go out and get some decent food.

233
00:16:00,861 --> 00:16:02,141
Can you forgive me?

234
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:04,901
Mom.

235
00:16:57,861 --> 00:16:58,981
Where's Rao Yuci?

236
00:17:06,621 --> 00:17:07,460
Bai Liangliang.

237
00:17:07,940 --> 00:17:09,061
What are you doing here?

238
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:10,781
I'm looking for Rao Yuci.

239
00:17:11,700 --> 00:17:12,581
Where is she?

240
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:15,460
Yuci truly

241
00:17:15,460 --> 00:17:17,141
saw you as a best friend.

242
00:17:17,581 --> 00:17:19,260
But look at what you did to her.

243
00:17:19,740 --> 00:17:21,381
You ruined her,

244
00:17:21,420 --> 00:17:22,381
and you've ruined

245
00:17:22,381 --> 00:17:23,581
our entire family.

246
00:17:23,781 --> 00:17:25,220
What else do you want?

247
00:17:26,061 --> 00:17:27,101
Listen up.

248
00:17:27,541 --> 00:17:28,781
You're not welcome here.

249
00:17:29,141 --> 00:17:30,341
Get out of here right now.

250
00:17:31,581 --> 00:17:32,260
Your whole family

251
00:17:32,260 --> 00:17:33,980
is really a piece of work.

252
00:17:35,341 --> 00:17:36,980
When Rao Yuci stabbed you in the back,

253
00:17:36,980 --> 00:17:38,381
you treated me like a daughter.

254
00:17:38,460 --> 00:17:39,460
And now?

255
00:17:40,980 --> 00:17:42,180
Now that I'm no longer useful,

256
00:17:42,180 --> 00:17:43,660
you're just chasing me out?

257
00:17:44,740 --> 00:17:45,740
Xu Zhaohe.

258
00:17:46,180 --> 00:17:47,101
You're just like

259
00:17:47,101 --> 00:17:48,940
your husband who got what he deserved.

260
00:17:49,381 --> 00:17:50,460
Just like your cold-blooded

261
00:17:50,460 --> 00:17:51,660
monster of a daughter.

262
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:53,180
Karma will come for you too!

263
00:17:53,821 --> 00:17:54,740
Bai Liangliang!

264
00:17:57,341 --> 00:17:59,500
You've truly lost your sense
of right and wrong.

265
00:18:00,061 --> 00:18:00,980
Yuci really

266
00:18:00,980 --> 00:18:02,821
treated you like a sister.

267
00:18:03,460 --> 00:18:04,260
She always

268
00:18:04,260 --> 00:18:05,861
thought of you, cared for you,

269
00:18:05,861 --> 00:18:07,781
and did everything
in her power to help you.

270
00:18:08,141 --> 00:18:09,541
Aside from your own mother,

271
00:18:09,541 --> 00:18:11,420
who else would ever treat you

272
00:18:11,420 --> 00:18:13,341
with such altruism?

273
00:18:13,341 --> 00:18:15,020
Who else would show you such kindness?

274
00:18:15,101 --> 00:18:16,220
Don't bring up my mother!

275
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:17,381
Don't you feel any guilt?

276
00:18:17,381 --> 00:18:18,220
Don't you dare!

277
00:18:18,220 --> 00:18:19,301
You have no right!

278
00:18:19,381 --> 00:18:20,660
Have you lost your mind?

279
00:18:20,660 --> 00:18:21,821
Yes, I've lost it!

280
00:18:22,381 --> 00:18:24,180
Rao Yuci drove me to this!

281
00:18:24,301 --> 00:18:26,301
Your daughter drove me insane!

282
00:18:28,901 --> 00:18:29,740
Where is she?

283
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:31,700
Where is she now?

284
00:18:32,141 --> 00:18:33,020
Answer me!

285
00:18:33,180 --> 00:18:34,061
I don't know.

286
00:18:34,341 --> 00:18:35,101
Even if I did,

287
00:18:35,101 --> 00:18:36,420
I would never tell you.

288
00:18:37,141 --> 00:18:38,381
I'm warning you.

289
00:18:38,581 --> 00:18:39,301
You better not

290
00:18:39,301 --> 00:18:40,740
hurt my daughter again,

291
00:18:41,101 --> 00:18:42,980
or I swear I'll make you pay!

292
00:18:43,901 --> 00:18:45,500
She's the one who hurt me first!

293
00:18:45,660 --> 00:18:47,061
She was the one!

294
00:18:47,341 --> 00:18:48,141
It was her!

295
00:18:53,060 --> 00:18:54,450
Bai Liangliang, what are you doing?

296
00:18:54,861 --> 00:18:55,861
This is a hospital!

297
00:18:56,420 --> 00:18:57,500
So what if it's a hospital?

298
00:18:58,020 --> 00:18:58,821
Look at them...

299
00:18:59,581 --> 00:19:01,220
They're all still alive!

300
00:19:02,301 --> 00:19:03,420
But what about my mom?

301
00:19:04,980 --> 00:19:06,381
My mother is dead!

302
00:19:06,980 --> 00:19:08,301
She's dead!

303
00:19:08,581 --> 00:19:10,101
(Medical Death Certificate)
Bai Xia is dead!

304
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:12,301
My mom is dead!

305
00:19:13,381 --> 00:19:15,301
And it's all Rao Yuci's fault!

306
00:19:18,821 --> 00:19:19,621
Chen Mo.

307
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:23,220
You tell Rao Yuci

308
00:19:23,821 --> 00:19:25,500
that I'll make her pay for this.

309
00:19:27,581 --> 00:19:28,500
And you too.

310
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:30,781
All of you...

311
00:19:32,621 --> 00:19:33,541
The pain

312
00:19:33,541 --> 00:19:35,141
you've caused me

313
00:19:35,341 --> 00:19:37,220
will be returned

314
00:19:37,220 --> 00:19:38,341
a hundredfold.

315
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:48,020
Go.

316
00:19:51,180 --> 00:19:52,581
Tell Yuci.

317
00:19:55,101 --> 00:19:55,901
Yuci.

318
00:19:56,500 --> 00:19:58,180
I know you don't want
to see me right now,

319
00:19:58,621 --> 00:20:00,260
but there's something you need to know.

320
00:20:02,901 --> 00:20:04,061
Ms. Bai Xia has passed away.

321
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:10,420
(Chen Mo)
Bai Liangliang confronted your mother,

322
00:20:11,690 --> 00:20:12,940
and threatened to take revenge.

323
00:20:15,020 --> 00:20:16,460
We're all really worried about you.

324
00:20:28,700 --> 00:20:31,820
(No. 88 Linwei Alley, Salted duck)

325
00:20:52,020 --> 00:20:53,740
(My foot was injured back then,)

326
00:20:53,821 --> 00:20:55,020
(so I couldn't work.)

327
00:20:56,020 --> 00:20:58,020
(Mr. Xu's small pension)

328
00:20:58,861 --> 00:20:59,901
(wasn't enough to cover)

329
00:20:59,901 --> 00:21:01,541
(the costs of his rehabilitation.)

330
00:21:03,940 --> 00:21:05,020
(I had no other choice)

331
00:21:05,560 --> 00:21:07,020
(but to go online and ask for help.)

332
00:21:09,740 --> 00:21:10,541
(Yuci,)

333
00:21:11,101 --> 00:21:12,101
(the money you sent us)

334
00:21:12,101 --> 00:21:13,381
(was a lifesaver)

335
00:21:13,381 --> 00:21:15,341
(for our family.)

336
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:49,180
I've cleaned the house for you,

337
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:50,740
and I've put

338
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:51,821
new bedding on your bed.

339
00:21:52,381 --> 00:21:53,861
Just make yourself at home.

340
00:21:54,460 --> 00:21:56,220
I'll make sure to pay rent on time.

341
00:21:56,700 --> 00:21:57,541
Don't worry about it.

342
00:21:58,260 --> 00:21:59,740
You've already helped us so much,

343
00:22:00,180 --> 00:22:01,980
how could we possibly take your money?

344
00:22:04,141 --> 00:22:05,861
I've kept

345
00:22:06,341 --> 00:22:07,541
your transfer receipts.

346
00:22:07,660 --> 00:22:09,020
Once I've saved up enough,

347
00:22:09,020 --> 00:22:10,260
I'll pay you back.

348
00:22:11,260 --> 00:22:12,980
Consider this place your home.

349
00:22:13,220 --> 00:22:14,821
Stay as long as you like.

350
00:22:16,460 --> 00:22:17,301
Get settled in.

351
00:22:17,301 --> 00:22:18,460
Dinner will be ready soon.

352
00:22:23,220 --> 00:22:24,020
Yuci?

353
00:22:25,821 --> 00:22:26,660
Ms. Bai Xia.

354
00:22:27,101 --> 00:22:27,781
I still have

355
00:22:27,781 --> 00:22:28,861
a bit more to do here.

356
00:22:28,861 --> 00:22:29,940
I've got duck meat for you.

357
00:22:29,940 --> 00:22:30,980
Go on and have some.

358
00:22:32,901 --> 00:22:34,141
When you're out there,

359
00:22:36,180 --> 00:22:37,541
don't skip your meals.

360
00:22:41,660 --> 00:22:43,260
Thank you, Ms. Bai Xia.

361
00:22:56,781 --> 00:22:57,621
Miss Rao.

362
00:22:57,861 --> 00:22:59,581
These are Ms. Bai Xia's belongings.

363
00:22:59,581 --> 00:23:00,940
Everything has been organized.

364
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:02,700
Please check and sign for them.

365
00:23:05,141 --> 00:23:05,940
Thank you.

366
00:23:06,420 --> 00:23:07,101
No problem.

367
00:23:07,101 --> 00:23:09,101
If you need anything else,
just let me know.

368
00:23:45,301 --> 00:23:46,460
Don't worry, Ms. Bai.

369
00:23:47,101 --> 00:23:48,020
Mr. Xu has already

370
00:23:48,020 --> 00:23:49,541
started his rehabilitation here.

371
00:23:52,301 --> 00:23:53,141
After Ms. Bai Xia

372
00:23:53,141 --> 00:23:54,821
brought Mr. Xu here the other day,

373
00:23:54,980 --> 00:23:56,460
she left your contact information.

374
00:23:56,861 --> 00:23:57,621
But we haven't

375
00:23:57,621 --> 00:23:58,781
seen her since.

376
00:23:58,901 --> 00:24:00,020
Is she away on a long trip?

377
00:24:03,061 --> 00:24:04,700
Mr. Xu will stay here for now.

378
00:24:05,061 --> 00:24:05,901
I've already prepaid

379
00:24:05,901 --> 00:24:07,301
three months of his medical fees.

380
00:24:08,740 --> 00:24:09,740
Understood, Ms. Bai.

381
00:24:27,180 --> 00:24:27,980
Liangliang.

382
00:24:30,020 --> 00:24:30,901
Mr. Xu.

383
00:24:32,541 --> 00:24:33,861
You helped me once.

384
00:24:35,101 --> 00:24:36,541
I won't turn my back on you.

385
00:24:37,901 --> 00:24:38,980
Things will stay the same.

386
00:24:39,861 --> 00:24:41,781
Your life won't be affected.

387
00:24:42,381 --> 00:24:43,061
Come on.

388
00:24:43,061 --> 00:24:43,821
Liangliang.

389
00:24:48,381 --> 00:24:50,621
Where is your mother?

390
00:25:04,301 --> 00:25:05,180
Where's your mom?

391
00:25:13,080 --> 00:25:13,980
Take care of yourself.

392
00:25:16,901 --> 00:25:17,700
It hurts.

393
00:25:25,381 --> 00:25:26,180
Liangliang.

394
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:29,740
It...

395
00:25:31,381 --> 00:25:32,180
hurts.

396
00:25:41,061 --> 00:25:43,420
When something starts out wrong,

397
00:25:44,581 --> 00:25:46,260
it just keeps going that way.

398
00:25:47,700 --> 00:25:48,821
I've tried,

399
00:25:50,180 --> 00:25:51,861
but I still can't understand it.

400
00:25:52,821 --> 00:25:53,940
I can't accept it.

401
00:26:00,861 --> 00:26:01,740
Mr. Xu.

402
00:26:03,020 --> 00:26:04,541
Do you ever get the feeling

403
00:26:05,220 --> 00:26:06,940
that I don't belong here at all?

404
00:26:08,260 --> 00:26:09,301
One day,

405
00:26:10,341 --> 00:26:11,781
I'm going to leave this place.

406
00:26:38,420 --> 00:26:39,581
(But don't you forget,)

407
00:26:40,101 --> 00:26:41,160
(you still have Chen Mo,)

408
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:42,500
(Yu Peidong,)

409
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:44,020
(and the entire Dept 3.)

410
00:26:46,020 --> 00:26:47,061
(And your parents.)

411
00:26:48,101 --> 00:26:48,980
(Even that tiny shop)

412
00:26:48,980 --> 00:26:49,940
(run by that deaf-mute.)

413
00:26:51,180 --> 00:26:52,301
I'll deal with them

414
00:26:52,301 --> 00:26:53,341
one by one.

415
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:55,460
No matter where I stand,

416
00:26:56,301 --> 00:26:57,381
I can make it happen.

417
00:27:02,861 --> 00:27:04,020
(So you're an idealist, huh?)

418
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:07,020
(Today, I'm going to show you)

419
00:27:08,061 --> 00:27:09,940
(the abyss your idealism)

420
00:27:09,940 --> 00:27:11,061
(will take you!)

421
00:27:13,341 --> 00:27:15,460
(I once charged
straight toward the light,)

422
00:27:17,141 --> 00:27:18,660
(only to be dragged into the abyss)

423
00:27:18,660 --> 00:27:19,781
(by the darkness.)

424
00:27:21,061 --> 00:27:22,180
(Scarred and broken,)

425
00:27:23,980 --> 00:27:25,301
(after everything I've endured,)

426
00:27:26,861 --> 00:27:28,341
(I now know my weaknesses,)

427
00:27:29,101 --> 00:27:30,141
(and just how small I am.)

428
00:27:31,740 --> 00:27:32,740
(But the person I am now)

429
00:27:34,020 --> 00:27:35,420
(is pained yet clear-headed.)

430
00:27:38,541 --> 00:27:39,460
(I believe)

431
00:27:40,260 --> 00:27:41,581
(that a mayfly can shake a tree,)

432
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:44,500
(and that evil cannot
run rampant forever.)

433
00:27:47,020 --> 00:27:48,220
(Between light and darkness,)

434
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,740
(someone must be
willing to take the risk.)

435
00:27:55,541 --> 00:27:56,621
(Regardless of the outcome,)

436
00:27:57,720 --> 00:27:59,420
(I've decided
to plunge into the darkness)

437
00:28:01,980 --> 00:28:03,220
(and see for myself)

438
00:28:04,901 --> 00:28:06,101
(what truly lies within.)

439
00:28:48,300 --> 00:28:50,061
I didn't realize
the injuries were this bad.

440
00:29:02,621 --> 00:29:03,420
Are you scared?

441
00:29:07,660 --> 00:29:08,460
I am.

442
00:29:10,581 --> 00:29:11,980
You've done so much for me.

443
00:29:11,980 --> 00:29:12,861
You must be back

444
00:29:13,541 --> 00:29:14,581
to oppose me.

445
00:29:17,940 --> 00:29:18,740
No.

446
00:29:20,460 --> 00:29:21,581
The warning you gave me

447
00:29:21,581 --> 00:29:23,020
was more than enough.

448
00:29:23,581 --> 00:29:24,821
I'm well aware

449
00:29:25,781 --> 00:29:27,301
that if I step out of line again,

450
00:29:29,821 --> 00:29:30,660
I will lose

451
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:32,020
absolutely everything I have.

452
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:38,180
You really are a little genius.

453
00:29:40,621 --> 00:29:41,420
However,

454
00:29:45,781 --> 00:29:47,180
I have no more use for you.

455
00:29:47,940 --> 00:29:49,940
Just because Li Wancheng let you back in,

456
00:29:51,500 --> 00:29:52,700
doesn't mean I'd trust you.

457
00:29:54,420 --> 00:29:57,020
You're out in the open, and so am I.

458
00:29:58,180 --> 00:29:58,940
I won't assign you

459
00:29:58,940 --> 00:30:00,260
any actual work.

460
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:08,341
I've had a change of heart, Mr. Jiang.

461
00:30:09,141 --> 00:30:10,220
You were right.

462
00:30:11,381 --> 00:30:13,180
Numbers are just a game.

463
00:30:14,180 --> 00:30:15,660
And if I want to achieve my dreams,

464
00:30:16,301 --> 00:30:17,980
I have to play the game to the end.

465
00:30:19,861 --> 00:30:21,020
You've already shown me

466
00:30:21,020 --> 00:30:22,301
who the winner is.

467
00:30:23,301 --> 00:30:24,821
Why wouldn't I follow your lead?

468
00:30:34,020 --> 00:30:35,061
Do you really think

469
00:30:36,260 --> 00:30:37,420
I'm that naive?

470
00:30:38,821 --> 00:30:39,700
What do you need

471
00:30:39,700 --> 00:30:40,861
me to do for you, Mr. Jiang?

472
00:30:41,621 --> 00:30:42,621
Just say the word.

473
00:30:45,101 --> 00:30:46,260
Shut down every project

474
00:30:46,260 --> 00:30:47,800
Yu Peidong and his team are working on.

475
00:30:50,141 --> 00:30:50,940
Why?

476
00:30:54,020 --> 00:30:55,460
Do I owe you an explanation?

477
00:30:57,781 --> 00:30:59,180
You misunderstand me, Mr. Jiang.

478
00:30:59,621 --> 00:31:00,781
It's just that these projects

479
00:31:00,781 --> 00:31:02,301
have already been halted once.

480
00:31:02,341 --> 00:31:03,781
If we restart them

481
00:31:04,020 --> 00:31:05,260
only to kill them again,

482
00:31:05,341 --> 00:31:06,061
I'm afraid it will

483
00:31:06,061 --> 00:31:07,341
trigger a backlash from the team.

484
00:31:16,781 --> 00:31:17,581
Ms. Ren.

485
00:31:17,900 --> 00:31:19,020
Please come in for a moment.

486
00:31:21,381 --> 00:31:22,180
Rao Yuci,

487
00:31:22,980 --> 00:31:23,940
you're a smart girl.

488
00:31:24,101 --> 00:31:24,901
I'm sure

489
00:31:24,980 --> 00:31:26,260
you can find a reason.

490
00:31:26,660 --> 00:31:27,821
Didn't you say

491
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,341
you came back to work for me?

492
00:31:31,341 --> 00:31:32,700
This will be your first assignment.

493
00:31:35,940 --> 00:31:36,980
Understood, Mr. Jiang.

494
00:31:38,980 --> 00:31:40,460
If anyone has an objection,

495
00:31:41,500 --> 00:31:42,700
process their resignation.

496
00:31:48,141 --> 00:31:48,940
Ms. Ren,

497
00:31:49,420 --> 00:31:50,220
please cooperate

498
00:31:50,220 --> 00:31:51,581
with Ms. Rao's upcoming work.

499
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:54,781
Yes, sir.

500
00:32:07,820 --> 00:32:11,780
(Three days ago)

501
00:32:14,901 --> 00:32:15,700
Qingyu.

502
00:32:16,460 --> 00:32:18,061
The Bai family has held on for so long

503
00:32:19,180 --> 00:32:21,381
thanks to years of your effort.

504
00:32:27,581 --> 00:32:28,381
Take care.

505
00:32:37,301 --> 00:32:39,180
After all that persuasion,

506
00:32:39,180 --> 00:32:41,101
he finally agreed to the partnership.

507
00:32:41,420 --> 00:32:42,541
I should thank you, Ms. Bai,

508
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,101
for giving me this opportunity.

509
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:46,781
But this is only a verbal commitment.

510
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:49,020
For this tripartite cooperation,

511
00:32:49,141 --> 00:32:51,141
we must hurry and sign the contract.

512
00:32:51,781 --> 00:32:53,740
We can't give him a chance to back out.

513
00:32:53,740 --> 00:32:54,460
Understood.

514
00:32:55,141 --> 00:32:56,700
When the financing conference begins,

515
00:32:56,861 --> 00:32:57,660
those investors

516
00:32:57,821 --> 00:32:58,541
will only cough up

517
00:32:58,541 --> 00:33:00,220
the hard cash once they see

518
00:33:00,301 --> 00:33:02,381
Yang Jinwan's face.

519
00:33:03,301 --> 00:33:06,260
Also, what's the deal with Rao Yuci?

520
00:33:08,301 --> 00:33:09,381
Don't you forget

521
00:33:10,260 --> 00:33:11,980
how my grandson died.

522
00:33:13,660 --> 00:33:14,460
I haven't forgotten,

523
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:16,660
nor would I ever dare to.

524
00:33:17,740 --> 00:33:18,740
Rest assured, Ms. Bai.

525
00:33:35,781 --> 00:33:37,061
Yuliang, you're in charge here.

526
00:33:37,101 --> 00:33:38,660
Stay at your designated spots.

527
00:33:38,660 --> 00:33:39,821
Qingqing, this side's yours.

528
00:33:39,830 --> 00:33:40,861
Qingqing, you're responsible for this.

529
00:33:40,861 --> 00:33:42,861
We should head to
those spots we agreed on, right?

530
00:33:42,861 --> 00:33:43,220
Right.

531
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:44,141
Listen for my signal.

532
00:33:44,141 --> 00:33:46,621
We'll go on three. One, two...

533
00:33:46,821 --> 00:33:47,420
Got it?

534
00:33:47,420 --> 00:33:48,700
- Mission accepted!
- Good.

535
00:33:49,180 --> 00:33:50,341
Now, break!

536
00:33:53,341 --> 00:33:54,141
Okay?

537
00:33:55,301 --> 00:33:56,101
Not bad.

538
00:33:56,220 --> 00:33:57,581
You've leaned into the theatrics.

539
00:33:57,581 --> 00:33:58,781
As for tonight...

540
00:33:58,781 --> 00:33:59,541
It's on me.

541
00:34:09,821 --> 00:34:10,620
Yuci.

542
00:34:10,980 --> 00:34:11,540
What happened

543
00:34:11,540 --> 00:34:12,661
these past few days?

544
00:34:20,140 --> 00:34:21,221
Peidong and I already know

545
00:34:21,301 --> 00:34:22,821
about your injuries.

546
00:34:25,580 --> 00:34:26,861
Was it Jiang Dongchao?

547
00:34:32,540 --> 00:34:33,821
I checked the surveillance.

548
00:34:34,620 --> 00:34:35,381
The night before

549
00:34:35,381 --> 00:34:36,381
you missed work,

550
00:34:36,701 --> 00:34:37,540
all the footage

551
00:34:37,540 --> 00:34:38,620
had been deleted.

552
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:39,980
Whatever happened to you,

553
00:34:40,300 --> 00:34:41,821
Jiang Dongchao is definitely behind it.

554
00:34:43,701 --> 00:34:44,580
Just tell me.

555
00:34:45,701 --> 00:34:46,620
Speak up.

556
00:34:47,181 --> 00:34:48,460
We'll find a way to help you.

557
00:34:54,420 --> 00:34:55,221
Ms. Ren.

558
00:34:56,301 --> 00:34:57,420
If you're going to keep

559
00:34:57,420 --> 00:34:58,940
talking about personal matters,

560
00:34:59,341 --> 00:35:00,060
we might as well

561
00:35:00,060 --> 00:35:01,341
head back to Mr. Jiang's office.

562
00:35:06,661 --> 00:35:08,181
You know how Yu Peidong is.

563
00:35:09,181 --> 00:35:10,821
If his projects are killed again,

564
00:35:10,980 --> 00:35:12,381
he's going to cause a scene.

565
00:35:12,781 --> 00:35:13,940
This is a company decision.

566
00:35:13,940 --> 00:35:14,741
But what about you?

567
00:35:16,261 --> 00:35:17,341
What's your decision?

568
00:35:23,741 --> 00:35:24,540
Yuci.

569
00:35:25,781 --> 00:35:27,701
Since you arrived,
so much has changed here.

570
00:35:29,020 --> 00:35:29,901
Everyone says

571
00:35:30,781 --> 00:35:32,701
there's no room
for heart at Lysen Group.

572
00:35:33,460 --> 00:35:34,620
But you changed that

573
00:35:34,901 --> 00:35:36,181
when you joined us.

574
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:39,140
I just want to know one thing.

575
00:35:40,140 --> 00:35:41,661
Is this really what you want?

576
00:35:54,100 --> 00:35:58,020
=Episode 25=
(What Lies in the Darkness)

577
00:35:58,540 --> 00:36:00,980
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

578
00:36:00,980 --> 00:36:07,180
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

579
00:36:07,940 --> 00:36:11,140
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

580
00:36:11,140 --> 00:36:15,660
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

581
00:36:15,660 --> 00:36:23,180
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

582
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:27,100
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

583
00:36:27,100 --> 00:36:31,140
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

584
00:36:31,140 --> 00:36:34,660
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

585
00:36:34,660 --> 00:36:38,620
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

586
00:36:38,620 --> 00:36:42,780
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

587
00:36:42,780 --> 00:36:46,980
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

588
00:36:46,980 --> 00:36:50,780
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

589
00:36:50,780 --> 00:36:54,860
♪Keep walking through the light♪

590
00:36:54,860 --> 00:36:59,060
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

591
00:36:59,060 --> 00:37:05,380
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

592
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:29,140
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

593
00:37:29,140 --> 00:37:32,980
♪An apology that came too late♪

594
00:37:32,980 --> 00:37:37,620
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

595
00:37:37,700 --> 00:37:45,100
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

596
00:37:45,100 --> 00:37:49,180
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

597
00:37:49,180 --> 00:37:53,260
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

598
00:37:53,260 --> 00:37:57,260
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

599
00:37:57,260 --> 00:38:01,020
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

600
00:38:01,020 --> 00:38:05,220
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

601
00:38:05,220 --> 00:38:09,380
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

602
00:38:09,380 --> 00:38:13,100
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

603
00:38:13,100 --> 00:38:17,140
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

604
00:38:17,140 --> 00:38:21,180
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

605
00:38:21,180 --> 00:38:27,380
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
